Package org.graphstream.util.time

Class Summary
ISODateComponent Defines components of ISODateIO.
ISODateComponent.AliasComponent Defines an alias component.
ISODateComponent.AMPMComponent Component handling AM/PM.
ISODateComponent.EpochComponent Component handling a number of milliseconds since the epoch (january, 1st 1970).
ISODateComponent.FieldComponent Defines a component associated with a field of a calendar.
ISODateComponent.NotImplementedComponent Defines a not implemented component.
ISODateComponent.TextComponent Defines a text component.
ISODateComponent.UTCOffsetComponent Component handling utc offset (+/- 0000).
ISODateIO Scanner for date in ISO/IEC 9899:1999 format.
